Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.53,English,,0,0,0,,- Can I tell you something I'm bad at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 可以告诉你一件我不擅长的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.50,English,,0,0,0,,I am terrible at making clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我非常不擅长当“标题党”。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.65,English,,0,0,0,,Up until two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在两年前那会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.11,English,,0,0,0,,my most popular video\Nwas about a basketball
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我最火的视频是一个关于把回旋的篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:12.01,English,,0,0,0,,being dropped from a dam\Nwith a bit of backspin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:12.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从水坝上扔下来的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.40,English,,0,0,0,,It takes off like a rocket and shoots out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,篮球像火箭一样发射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:16.56,English,,0,0,0,,way further than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:16.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比你想象的远得多。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.19,English,,0,0,0,,This video was embedded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:20.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个视频被嵌入到几百个新闻网站中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.70,English,,0,0,0,,on literally hundreds of news websites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:25.32,English,,0,0,0,,And in its first week, it\Ngot 16.3 million views,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:25.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在视频发出一个星期内获得了一千六百万次浏览，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:29.20,English,,0,0,0,,but almost none of those views\Ncame on the YouTube platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:29.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但几乎没有浏览是来自 YouTube 平台本身。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.13,English,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.56,English,,0,0,0,,Because I gave it this thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.56,English,,0,0,0,,因为这是我给它的封面，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.91,English,,0,0,0,,and I called it "Strange\NApplications of the Magnus Effect."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且我把这个视频取名为”马格努斯效应的奇怪应用“。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:39.63,English,,0,0,0,,This video is sponsored by KiwiCo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.12,English,,0,0,0,,More about them at the end of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.61,English,,0,0,0,,Now, I believe within YouTube,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我相信，我现在在 YouTube 被认作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:47.24,English,,0,0,0,,I'm used as an example of how\Nnot to package your video.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:47.24,English,,0,0,0,,不去”包装“自己视频的典型例子。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.88,English,,0,0,0,,As if to demonstrate just how bad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:53.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有一个人重新上传了这一视频并\N将它取名为”从水坝扔下的篮球“
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.32,English,,0,0,0,,a title and thumbnail this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.13,English,,0,0,0,,someone else re-uploaded the\Nvideo with the clever title,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.55,English,,0,0,0,,"Basketball Dropped From Dam."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就像是为了凸显原来的标题和封面有多烂。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:58.24,English,,0,0,0,,And within a few weeks,\Nthat video had received
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:58.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几个星期内，这个视频就在 YouTube 上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:01.01,English,,0,0,0,,tens of millions of views on YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:01.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,获得了几千万浏览。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.41,English,,0,0,0,,This is when YouTube gave\Nme access to ContentID.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这时候 YouTube 给了我 ContentID 的使用权限。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.56,English,,0,0,0,,That's the system that\Nallows you to earn revenue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:08.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个系统能够让你在别人转载你的视频时赚取收益。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.89,English,,0,0,0,,when someone else re-uploads\Nyour videos, which was good,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:11.74,English,,0,0,0,,but I still wasn't very good at clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:11.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这很不错，但我还是不擅长当标题党。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.73,English,,0,0,0,,So for this video, I called in an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以制作这期视频时，我请了一位专家。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.65,English,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see your reaction face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想看看你的震惊脸。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:17.97,English,,0,0,0,,Can you give me like a reaction face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:17.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能否让我看看你的震惊脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.10,English,,0,0,0,,Like what's a good thumbnail face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如一个适合作为封面的表情长什么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.15,English,,0,0,0,,- Oh, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦，我明白你的意思了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:22.09,English,,0,0,0,,This is a thumbnail face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:22.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是一个用作封面的表情。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:24.22,English,,0,0,0,,(Derek laughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:24.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Derek 大笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.28,English,,0,0,0,,I have like 10, I go through\Nthe motions of like...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.28,English,,0,0,0,,我有十个这样的表情，就比如像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:30.06,English,,0,0,0,,(Derek laughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:30.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Derek 大笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.06,English,,0,0,0,,And then we just take the best one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我们选择最好的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.56,English,,0,0,0,,I probably have like\N500 of these just saved
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我大概存了五百个像那样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.29,English,,0,0,0,,and we can just Photoshop\Nmy face on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我们直接 PS 这些表情。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.36,English,,0,0,0,,That way, I don't have to do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样我就不用再做表情了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:41.46,English,,0,0,0,,- When I started on this\Nplatform, some 10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:41.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约十年前，当我刚加入这个平台时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:43.12,English,,0,0,0,,clickbait was less important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:43.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,标题和封面没那么重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.09,English,,0,0,0,,Subscribers were what mattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,重要的是关注，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.80,English,,0,0,0,,because most of the views\Ncame from the sub feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为大部分的点击都来自向关注者的推送。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.48,English,,0,0,0,,And videos went viral usually
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:51.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,视频爆红一般是靠其他地方的流量，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.09,English,,0,0,0,,by getting a lot of attention elsewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.00,English,,0,0,0,,like on Reddit or Facebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如 Reddit 和 Facebook，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.86,English,,0,0,0,,not due to the YouTube algorithm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而不是靠 YouTube 的算法。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.81,English,,0,0,0,,But once you had a big\Nvideo and people subscribed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但一旦你有了一个比较火的视频，吸引人们关注，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.08,English,,0,0,0,,well, then your next video\Nwould likely get a lot of views
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那你的下一个视频很可能就会从关注者那里得到很多浏览。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:01.28,English,,0,0,0,,from those subscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.21,English,,0,0,0,,So YouTube would take that popular video
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,于是 YouTube 就会把热门的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:04.42,English,,0,0,0,,and share it with more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:04.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,分享给更多人。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.72,English,,0,0,0,,And so you'd get more subscribers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样你会获得更多的关注者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.24,English,,0,0,0,,in a positive feedback loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,形成一个正反馈循环。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:12.02,English,,0,0,0,,But soon, YouTube realized\Nthat this did not create
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:12.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但很快，YouTube 认识到这样不能为观众
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.11,English,,0,0,0,,the best experience for the viewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,提供一个最优的体验。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.05,English,,0,0,0,,They discovered that\Nshowing people only videos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:20.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们发现，光给人们展示他们订阅频道的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:20.24,English,,0,0,0,,from channels they were\Nsubscribed to led to fewer clicks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,导致整个网站作为一个整体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.69,English,,0,0,0,,less watch time and less engagement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,点击数、观看时间、互动量较少。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.25,English,,0,0,0,,with the site as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.25,English,,0,0,0,,Plus, they knew that\Nrelying on other platforms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,况且，他们知道依靠其他平台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.80,English,,0,0,0,,to drive traffic to viral hits was risky,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,引导流量创造爆红视频有风险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.56,English,,0,0,0,,since those other platforms might disable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为这些平台可以随时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.23,English,,0,0,0,,the traffic at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,砍掉这些流量。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.99,English,,0,0,0,,So they needed to make YouTube\Na destination in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以他们要让 YouTube 本身成为流量目的地。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.00,English,,0,0,0,,They wanted people to come to YouTube,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们希望人们来到 YouTube，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.90,English,,0,0,0,,see videos that interested them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看他们感兴趣的视频，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.62,English,,0,0,0,,click on at least one of them\Nand watch it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,点击其中至少一个视频并看一段时间。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.43,English,,0,0,0,,Ideally get sucked down\Nthe YouTube rabbit hole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最好掉进 YouTube 的陷阱里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.77,English,,0,0,0,,and spend hours on the site\Nwithout even noticing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不知不觉地在网站上花费数个小时。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.96,English,,0,0,0,,The ultimate resource is people's time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最终极的资源还是人们的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.62,English,,0,0,0,,and attention, and every platform
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和注意力，而每个平台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:56.43,English,,0,0,0,,is trying to capture as\Nmuch of it as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:56.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,都希望获取尽可能多的资源。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:58.69,English,,0,0,0,,So, to make YouTube\Nthis go-to destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:58.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，为了让 YouTube 成为这个目的地，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.42,English,,0,0,0,,they had decrease the\Nimportance of subscribers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们减少了关注的重要性，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.16,English,,0,0,0,,make it less like a podcast app
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让它不像一个播客应用那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.16,English,,0,0,0,,where you only get the\Nshows you're subscribed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只能收听你已经关注的节目，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.53,English,,0,0,0,,and more like Reddit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而是更像 Reddit，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.26,English,,0,0,0,,where stuff with the most\Nengagement rises to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,互动最多的东西被顶到最前面。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:12.43,English,,0,0,0,,But that necessarily meant increasing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:14.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但那必然意味着提高标题和封面的重要性。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.74,English,,0,0,0,,the importance of clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.85,English,,0,0,0,,Now, there seems to be a paradox\Nwhen it comes to clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但关于”标题党“却有一个矛盾。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:21.13,English,,0,0,0,,People almost universally\Nclaim to hate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:21.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几乎所有人都声称自己讨厌它，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.85,English,,0,0,0,,but you also see it everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但你在哪里都能看到它。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.60,English,,0,0,0,,So why is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那这是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.74,English,,0,0,0,,Well, one of the problems\Nis we don't all agree
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，一个问题是我们没有在”标题党“
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.39,English,,0,0,0,,on the definition of clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,的定义上达成一致。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.90,English,,0,0,0,,When I google it, the top definition is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我去搜索它时，第一条定义是，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:34.24,English,,0,0,0,,on the internet, content\Nwhose main purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:36.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在互联网上，用于吸引注意力、鼓励访客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.79,English,,0,0,0,,is to attract attention\Nand encourage visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:39.36,English,,0,0,0,,to click on a link to\Na particular webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:39.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,点击某个网页链接的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.05,English,,0,0,0,,We could call this type I clickbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以把它叫做”Ⅰ类标题党“，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.41,English,,0,0,0,,and there doesn't seem to\Nbe anything wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且它本身似乎没有什么错。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.98,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you didn't\Ntry to attract attention
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，如果你不去吸引注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.28,English,,0,0,0,,and get people to click on your links,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并让人们点击你的链接，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.40,English,,0,0,0,,then you wouldn't really\Nbe doing your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那等于没做你该做的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.29,English,,0,0,0,,But there is a second definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但它还有第二种定义。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.95,English,,0,0,0,,One that I think more people ascribe to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一种我认为有更多人理解的定义。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.41,English,,0,0,0,,which is something such\Nas a headline designed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:59.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一个让读者想去点击网页链接的东西，比如标题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:59.76,English,,0,0,0,,to make readers want to\Nclick on a hyperlink,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.82,English,,0,0,0,,especially when the link leads to content
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.82,English,,0,0,0,,尤其是链接到内容可疑的网页时。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.28,English,,0,0,0,,of dubious value or interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.09,English,,0,0,0,,Wikipedia says, "A defining\Ncharacteristic of clickbait
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,维基百科说：”标题党的一个根本特征是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.98,English,,0,0,0,,is that it is sensationalized\Nor misleading."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,情绪化或有误导性。“
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.82,English,,0,0,0,,And it also talks about teasers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它还提到了一种标题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.52,English,,0,0,0,,that intentionally withhold information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,故意去隐藏信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.64,English,,0,0,0,,to exploit the "curiosity gap."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来利用你的好奇心。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.20,English,,0,0,0,,They give you enough\Ninformation to make you curious,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它给你足够多的信息来激发你的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.33,English,,0,0,0,,but not enough to satisfy that curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但不足以满足你的好奇。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.06,English,,0,0,0,,Here are two actual titles\Nfrom a news website.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这里是某新闻网站上的两个标题。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.73,English,,0,0,0,,Nine out of 10 Americans\Nare completely wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:30.20,English,,0,0,0,,《十个美国人有九个完全搞错了\N这一惊人的事实》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.20,English,,0,0,0,,about this mind blowing fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.63,English,,0,0,0,,And someone gave some kids some scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:34.92,English,,0,0,0,,《一个人给一些孩子几把剪刀，接下来发生了这些》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.92,English,,0,0,0,,Here's what happened next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.95,English,,0,0,0,,I think we can all agree\Nthat these are examples
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们都会认可它们属于
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.45,English,,0,0,0,,of bad type II clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,坏的第二类标题党。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:42.17,English,,0,0,0,,Now, imagine a clickbait\Nspace where on one axis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.63,English,,0,0,0,,you have how misleading\Nor sensationalized it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.63,English,,0,0,0,,And on the other, how much information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.88,English,,0,0,0,,is intentionally withheld\Nto create a curiosity gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.18,English,,0,0,0,,Well, then these two titles\Nfall in the top right corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.74,English,,0,0,0,,And these are the zones\Nof type II clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:58.71,English,,0,0,0,,At the other extreme,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:02.73,English,,0,0,0,,you have things that are so\Nunsensationalized as to be dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:05.55,English,,0,0,0,,You could call this the dead zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.72,English,,0,0,0,,Now, here is where you would find
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.65,English,,0,0,0,,"Strange applications\Nof the Magnus Effect."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.75,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, I didn't tell you\Nwhat the applications were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.98,English,,0,0,0,,Now, in the middle is where you\Nwould find type I clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.23,English,,0,0,0,,But honestly, I think type\NI and type II clickbait
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.44,English,,0,0,0,,are so different, that\Nwe shouldn't even use
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.99,English,,0,0,0,,the same word for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.60,English,,0,0,0,,Instead of type I clickbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:29.44,English,,0,0,0,,my friend and YouTuber, Brady\NHeron suggested legitbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:33.31,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, it might sound\Nenticing, but it is legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.73,English,,0,0,0,,Instead of type II clickbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:39.73,English,,0,0,0,,we could use clicktrap,\Nclicktrick, linktrap or dupechute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.94,English,,0,0,0,,What's important to recognize\Nis that for any given video,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.17,English,,0,0,0,,there is no one true title and thumbnail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.76,English,,0,0,0,,Each video could have\Nhundreds or thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.76,English,,0,0,0,,of different legitbait titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.07,English,,0,0,0,,For example, how does a zero-G plane work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:58.44,English,,0,0,0,,I went on a plane that does\Nparabolic trajectories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.97,English,,0,0,0,,What happens to fire on a zero-G plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.16,English,,0,0,0,,Now, the most enticing\Ntitles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:07.15,English,,0,0,0,,are found close to type II clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.56,English,,0,0,0,,I'm reminded of the infographic\Nby smarter every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.27,English,,0,0,0,,showing that on social media,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.62,English,,0,0,0,,the greatest engagement\Noccurs close to the boundary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.95,English,,0,0,0,,of what's allowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.43,English,,0,0,0,,But remember that everyone's\Ndefinition of clickbait
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.26,English,,0,0,0,,is different, and everyone's perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.97,English,,0,0,0,,of words and images are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.85,English,,0,0,0,,So these are not clear boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.20,English,,0,0,0,,They're actually kind of fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.27,English,,0,0,0,,What for one person might be legitbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.24,English,,0,0,0,,for someone else, could be a clicktrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.04,English,,0,0,0,,What's clear is that on a site
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.96,English,,0,0,0,,where click-through rate is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.27,English,,0,0,0,,clickbait of all types is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.76,English,,0,0,0,,How important to a video's success
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.00,English,,0,0,0,,is the title and thumbnail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.43,English,,0,0,0,,- Very important. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:42.26,English,,0,0,0,,If they don't click on the video,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.43,English,,0,0,0,,they don't watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.90,English,,0,0,0,,You can't get 10 million views
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.10,English,,0,0,0,,unless 10 million people\Nclick on the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.93,English,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, it's literally that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.63,English,,0,0,0,,They don't click on it,\Nthey don't watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.09,English,,0,0,0,,- So, why is clickbait everywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.30,English,,0,0,0,,Well, because it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.70,English,,0,0,0,,More enticing thumbnails get more clicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.23,English,,0,0,0,,Despite some people's claims
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.43,English,,0,0,0,,that they won't click or they'll unsub,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.95,English,,0,0,0,,it's just like evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:09.10,English,,0,0,0,,Whatever survives, multiplies\Nand traits become amplified.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.72,English,,0,0,0,,If you don't begrudge\Nthe giraffe its long neck
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.63,English,,0,0,0,,so it can reach the highest leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.07,English,,0,0,0,,can you begrudge a YouTuber the red arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.87,English,,0,0,0,,that allows them to\Nreach further audiences?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.00,English,,0,0,0,,I talked about this in\Nmy video two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.54,English,,0,0,0,,To be successful as a YouTuber,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.44,English,,0,0,0,,you need to optimize two things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.14,English,,0,0,0,,watch time and the click-through\Nrate of your videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.46,English,,0,0,0,,That's the number of times
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.73,English,,0,0,0,,the title and thumbnail are clicked,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.00,English,,0,0,0,,divided by the total number\Nof times they're shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.13,English,,0,0,0,,That's the number of impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:34.96,English,,0,0,0,,Now at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.14,English,,0,0,0,,this was something of a revelation for me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.91,English,,0,0,0,,because I always thought my\Njob was to make great videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.21,English,,0,0,0,,And then a title and thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.84,English,,0,0,0,,that adequately represented\Nwhat the video was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.64,English,,0,0,0,,But now I've realized that\Nmaking the title and thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:49.22,English,,0,0,0,,is at least half the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.57,English,,0,0,0,,This is not just because\Nbetter titles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.70,English,,0,0,0,,get you more clicks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.14,English,,0,0,0,,but because better titles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:57.16,English,,0,0,0,,will get you way more impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,YouTube has limited real estate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.28,English,,0,0,0,,with which to show you\Nvirtually infinite content.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.35,English,,0,0,0,,And so it's not enough\Nto make a good video
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.13,English,,0,0,0,,even if people watch all of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.27,English,,0,0,0,,you also have to make\Na title and thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.14,English,,0,0,0,,that gets clicked,\Nespecially in competition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:12.70,English,,0,0,0,,with other really good\Ntitles and thumbnails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.44,English,,0,0,0,,That's the only way you can expect YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.54,English,,0,0,0,,to give you more impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.28,English,,0,0,0,,Now, the big development\Nsince my last video on this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.78,English,,0,0,0,,is YouTube introduced real-time metrics
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:24.30,English,,0,0,0,,like views, impressions\Nand click-through rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.77,English,,0,0,0,,Now, I suggested this\Nwould create an arms race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.47,English,,0,0,0,,So what you can bet will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.68,English,,0,0,0,,is that creators will launch a video
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:31.69,English,,0,0,0,,and then they'll be sitting there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.64,English,,0,0,0,,with all these different\Nvariants of thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.38,English,,0,0,0,,and they'll be swapping them out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:38.03,English,,0,0,0,,and looking at what that\Ndoes to click-through rate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.74,English,,0,0,0,,and then going with the one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.61,English,,0,0,0,,that leads to the greatest\Nclick-through rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.21,English,,0,0,0,,And this is basically what has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.41,English,,0,0,0,,Let me give you my favorite example.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.02,English,,0,0,0,,Last year, I made a video about asteroids,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.71,English,,0,0,0,,which I thought was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.93,English,,0,0,0,,I called it "Asteroids:\NEarth's Biggest Threat,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.65,English,,0,0,0,,which is something Stephen Hawking said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.93,English,,0,0,0,,And people were very\Npositive about the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.20,English,,0,0,0,,They thought it was maybe one of my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.95,English,,0,0,0,,but the performance\Nwas well below average.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.72,English,,0,0,0,,In its first day,\Nasteroids was ranked ninth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.08,English,,0,0,0,,out of my previous 10 videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.48,English,,0,0,0,,It was probably on target
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.07,English,,0,0,0,,for about one and a half million views.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.27,English,,0,0,0,,So I tried different titles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:18.13,English,,0,0,0,,like, "Asteroid Impact:\NWhat Are Our Chances?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.82,English,,0,0,0,,Or "Asteroid Impact: What Could We Do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:23.85,English,,0,0,0,,But none of these changes\Ngot much traction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.52,English,,0,0,0,,And then on day three after launch,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.01,English,,0,0,0,,I changed the title and thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:30.65,English,,0,0,0,,to "These Are the\NAsteroids to Worry About."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:33.48,English,,0,0,0,,And immediately the video\Nstarted doing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.98,English,,0,0,0,,It quickly shot up from almost\Nmy worst performing video
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.72,English,,0,0,0,,to my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.03,English,,0,0,0,,It now has 14 million views.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.79,English,,0,0,0,,Nothing about the video changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:47.13,English,,0,0,0,,just that one image and 38 characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.18,English,,0,0,0,,But because of that, the video has reached
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:52.82,English,,0,0,0,,nearly 10 times as many people\Nas it otherwise would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.10,English,,0,0,0,,And the title and thumbnail\Naccurately describe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.49,English,,0,0,0,,what the video is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.70,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, sure, there's a curiosity gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.74,English,,0,0,0,,but you couldn't explain the whole concept
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.55,English,,0,0,0,,in the length of the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.55,English,,0,0,0,,So if you see a YouTuber\Nchanging titles and thumbnails,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.07,English,,0,0,0,,this is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:10.25,English,,0,0,0,,Because that effort can be\Nrewarded many times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.02,English,,0,0,0,,I've seen people\Nobjecting to this practice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.38,English,,0,0,0,,because they think the creator
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.73,English,,0,0,0,,is trying to dupe their audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.70,English,,0,0,0,,get them to click on the\Nsame video more than once,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.78,English,,0,0,0,,but that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.41,English,,0,0,0,,The whole point is to get YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.61,English,,0,0,0,,to show the title and\Nthumbnail to more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:25.65,English,,0,0,0,,We're trying to increase\Nthe number of impressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:28.63,English,,0,0,0,,which is heavily dependent\Non the click-through rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.47,English,,0,0,0,,Now, a lot of my recent videos\Nhave this typical view curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.69,English,,0,0,0,,There's an initial spike\Nafter I release the video
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.02,English,,0,0,0,,and then a dip, and then a second bump
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:40.13,English,,0,0,0,,after I have figured out a\Nbetter title and thumbnail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.58,English,,0,0,0,,I change the title and thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.15,English,,0,0,0,,and I watch the real time view graph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.48,English,,0,0,0,,What I'm looking for is a\Nnoticeable bump in views.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:51.05,English,,0,0,0,,Sometimes there's no change,\Nsometimes it gets worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.72,English,,0,0,0,,but on occasions, when you\Nsee something like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.52,English,,0,0,0,,well then, you know you've found a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.81,English,,0,0,0,,This is something all the\Nbig YouTubers are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.43,English,,0,0,0,,Not even Mr. Beast knows exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.89,English,,0,0,0,,which thumbnail will work best beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.74,English,,0,0,0,,Have you ever changed\Na title and thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.58,English,,0,0,0,,and then the video did better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.76,English,,0,0,0,,- Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.29,English,,0,0,0,,So everybody, I usually make\Nlike two or three thumbnails,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.00,English,,0,0,0,,and then if it's not\Ndoing as well as I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:15.26,English,,0,0,0,,we usually just swap 'em out\Nand see if it does better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.70,English,,0,0,0,,'cause the thing is like,\Nyou don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:21.19,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, you could know if you\Njust were an almighty being
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.80,English,,0,0,0,,that could just predict what\Npeople would be interested in,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.28,English,,0,0,0,,but you know, usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.35,English,,0,0,0,,Like, you can do hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.81,English,,0,0,0,,You don't really know if\Nlike you hiding in a tree
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.85,English,,0,0,0,,and then someone walking\Nbelow you is a good thumbnail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.35,English,,0,0,0,,Or if you hiding a trash can and\Nthem walking in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.75,English,,0,0,0,,So, you know, just do both
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.21,English,,0,0,0,,and then see which one interests\Npeople a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.04,English,,0,0,0,,- I feel the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:40.19,English,,0,0,0,,but I do feel like you have a better sense
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.08,English,,0,0,0,,of this than like most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.91,English,,0,0,0,,- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.59,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, no one gets 40\Nmillion views a video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:47.30,English,,0,0,0,,(both laughing)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.36,English,,0,0,0,,- But what is the point\Nin getting more views?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.19,English,,0,0,0,,If you're cynical,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.81,English,,0,0,0,,you might say it's all\Nabout money and fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.08,English,,0,0,0,,And while there are certainly\Nfinancial incentives
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.86,English,,0,0,0,,to getting more views,\Nthat's not why I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.36,English,,0,0,0,,As an educational YouTuber,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.37,English,,0,0,0,,I think there are two very good reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.84,English,,0,0,0,,for using excellent type I clickbait
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.11,English,,0,0,0,,over more straightforward packaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.55,English,,0,0,0,,To understand the first reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.71,English,,0,0,0,,let's consider two\Ndifferent possible titles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.36,English,,0,0,0,,for my most recent video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:16.02,English,,0,0,0,,I called it "The Simplest Math\NProblem No One Can Solve,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.35,English,,0,0,0,,but it's a video about\Nthe Collatz conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.47,English,,0,0,0,,So perhaps a more straightforward title
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.81,English,,0,0,0,,would have been simply to call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:24.57,English,,0,0,0,,The problem is, if I publish a video
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.50,English,,0,0,0,,called the Collatz conjecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.45,English,,0,0,0,,the most likely people to click on it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:31.64,English,,0,0,0,,are those who already know\Nwhat the Collatz conjecture is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.75,English,,0,0,0,,And the vast majority of people\Nwill never have heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.21,English,,0,0,0,,So for them, the title is meaningless
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.02,English,,0,0,0,,and only the very curious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.80,English,,0,0,0,,or those who really like\NVeritasium would click.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.23,English,,0,0,0,,In contrast, calling it\N"The Simplest Math Problem
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.83,English,,0,0,0,,No One Can Solve,"\Nconveys more information
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.80,English,,0,0,0,,about the video to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.78,English,,0,0,0,,And this means more\Npeople can click on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.28,English,,0,0,0,,most of whom will never have heard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.32,English,,0,0,0,,of the Collatz conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.85,English,,0,0,0,,So I get to teach them something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.79,English,,0,0,0,,And since the video has a\Nhigher click-through rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.00,English,,0,0,0,,YouTube shows it to even more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.11,English,,0,0,0,,So if my aim is to increase\Nthe level of knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.94,English,,0,0,0,,in the world by the\Nmaximum amount possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.66,English,,0,0,0,,this is the way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.05,English,,0,0,0,,The second reason we need to\Noptimize titles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.92,English,,0,0,0,,is to support the major\Ngoal of this channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.12,English,,0,0,0,,We are trying to make\Nthe best science films
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.04,English,,0,0,0,,on every topic we tackle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.48,English,,0,0,0,,That means traveling to meet\Nexperts in film experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.41,English,,0,0,0,,hiring people to build props,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:28.42,English,,0,0,0,,make spectacular animations,\Nresearch and fact check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.32,English,,0,0,0,,We hire expert consultants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.70,English,,0,0,0,,to double and triple check our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.11,English,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna make vlogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.26,English,,0,0,0,,I wanna make science\Ndocumentaries on YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:38.22,English,,0,0,0,,that put broadcast to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.48,English,,0,0,0,,And to make this possible and sustainable,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且为了让这个目标能够实现且能长期保持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.36,English,,0,0,0,,the videos have to get\Nviews and lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的视频就要有播放量 而且是非常多的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.74,English,,0,0,0,,And to do that, we have to make
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么既然要这么做 那我们就得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.36,English,,0,0,0,,the best titles and thumbnails we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想出足够好的标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.59,English,,0,0,0,,YouTuber and Patreon CEO, Jack Conte
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Jack Conte, Patreon 的 CEO，也是一位 YouTuber,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.00,English,,0,0,0,,has talked about adjusting your packaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,讲到了关于如何包装视频的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.31,English,,0,0,0,,The idea is know what\Nyou're passionate about,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,具体的意思是指 要清楚你最热衷于什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.00,English,,0,0,0,,what you won't compromise on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不会对什么妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.27,English,,0,0,0,,and that stuff goes in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把这些核心的东西装在盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.74,English,,0,0,0,,All the rest, like what\Npaper it's wrapped in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其余的那些 比如用什么样的纸来包这个盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.19,English,,0,0,0,,that's the packaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是包装的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.78,English,,0,0,0,,So the video is my focus\Nand the title and thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那就可以这么讲，视频内容是我最专注的，而标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.11,English,,0,0,0,,are the packaging that\NI'm happy to adjust,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,则是视频的漂亮包装 我可以随意去调整它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.20,English,,0,0,0,,so I can make the type of\Nvideos that are important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如此一来 我才能制作出我心目中地位甚高的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.59,English,,0,0,0,,Now, is it ironic that a\Nchannel whose whole purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么 如果现在有个频道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.42,English,,0,0,0,,is to promote a true seeking mindset
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它旨在为人们培养求真心理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.17,English,,0,0,0,,has to experiment at the\Nedge of what is truthful
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但它得在真理的边缘疯狂地不计后果地试探
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.94,English,,0,0,0,,in order to fulfill that purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来达到它的目的，这不是很讽刺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.92,English,,0,0,0,,It is something that I\Noften worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我通常会担心到的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.88,English,,0,0,0,,You know, when I did like\Nrisking my life to do X,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你知道，当我确实喜欢冒险去做一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.48,English,,0,0,0,,it's like, well, what probability of death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那时候我就想着“行吧 得有多大可能会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.39,English,,0,0,0,,does there have to be for\Nyou to risk your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才会让我冒生命危险去做这个事情呢”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.95,English,,0,0,0,,Like 50%?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如 50%？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.69,English,,0,0,0,,- I love how he always overthinks things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我很喜欢的是 他总会把事情想的很复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.95,English,,0,0,0,,(laughs)\NThat's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,（笑）真的很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.43,English,,0,0,0,,He's like, is my life risked enough
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他就这么想的“我是不是已经快到没命的边缘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.52,English,,0,0,0,,where I can put I risked my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以才来冒生命危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.25,English,,0,0,0,,I only had a 9% chance of dying
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我大概只有 9% 的可能会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.20,English,,0,0,0,,and I need at least a 13% chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我需要它至少是 13%”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.35,English,,0,0,0,,You're so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这也太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.95,English,,0,0,0,,He was the same way two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,两年前他也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.19,English,,0,0,0,,when he asked me all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问的我这些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:49.69,English,,0,0,0,,I was like, "Dude, just do\Nwhatever makes the most sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:49.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我那时就想“得了吧小伙子 干点有意义的事情它不好吗”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:52.39,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I mean, obviously\NI feel like my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:52.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 嗯，确实，是说我有时候觉得我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.59,English,,0,0,0,,are not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并不是那么准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.53,English,,0,0,0,,But what I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我后来意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.43,English,,0,0,0,,is that I don't have\Nto trust my instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我并不需要相信我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:01.46,English,,0,0,0,,This problem of getting the\Nbest title and thumbnail,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:01.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,关于什么样的封面和标题可以吸引眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.70,English,,0,0,0,,well, it's a scientific problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,实际上 这是个比较科学的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.74,English,,0,0,0,,We're just asking which accurate\Nrepresentation of the video
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问题其实就是 怎样准确地描述这个视频
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.61,English,,0,0,0,,will get the most clicks\Nfrom a general audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才能有更高的可能让普通大众点进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.73,English,,0,0,0,,And that's a problem we can use
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是我们可以用科学方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.81,English,,0,0,0,,the scientific method to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来解决的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.78,English,,0,0,0,,So I've hired a couple\Nof really bright people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我请来了几个有头脑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.74,English,,0,0,0,,and we spend a lot of time brainstorming
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一起花了很久的时间进行大脑风暴 集思广益
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.62,English,,0,0,0,,and making titles and\Nthumbnails and testing them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想出有意思的标题和封面 并把它们用在视频上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.77,English,,0,0,0,,For example, on Twitter and Patreon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如在 Twitter 和 Patreon 上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.09,English,,0,0,0,,Varitasium titles and\Nthumbnails have gotten better,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们的标题和封面的点子越来越惊奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.97,English,,0,0,0,,not because I'm better at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不是因为我在这方面更上手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.53,English,,0,0,0,,but because of my team and our testing.
