Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.86,English,,0,0,0,,The results have often\Ncontradicted what I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过有时候结果和我的期望恰好相反
