Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:40.75,English,,0,0,0,,when we excluded the word\Nsurprising from the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:40.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从标题里面拿掉之后 播放量较之前多了 10%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:44.50,English,,0,0,0,,So it became simply The Secret of Synchronization.
