Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.48,English,,0,0,0,,I thought these two titles were basically a toss up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我原以为这两个标题就是个二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:51.22,English,,0,0,0,,but Patreon had a strong\Npreference for one over the other.
