Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.96,English,,0,0,0,,What's interesting about this research
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而对于这个研究 非常有趣的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.02,English,,0,0,0,,is that the more clickable\Ntitles and thumbnails
