Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.90,English,,0,0,0,,One thing I didn't expect\Nwhen YouTube brought in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在 YouTube 上线实时统计数据分析功能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.42,English,,0,0,0,,the real time analytics tools
