Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.93,English,,0,0,0,,and allowed title and thumbnail changes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来获得人们印象的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:06.66,English,,0,0,0,,to affect impressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:06.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我没想到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:09.40,English,,0,0,0,,was that it would also\Nwork for older videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:09.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,老视频同样可以这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.12,English,,0,0,0,,So here is an old video\Nthat I originally entitled,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我最初给一个老视频起的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:15.52,English,,0,0,0,,"Why the Neutron is the\NHero of Nuclear Physics."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:15.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“中子为何是核物理之英雄”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.84,English,,0,0,0,,In hindsight, it's a weird,\Nkinda meaningless title.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,事后看来 这个标题显得很奇怪且毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:21.60,English,,0,0,0,,So I changed it to, "Why Einstein Thought
